dmca.title: For legal reasons, we've excluded from our search results content located at or under
dmca.body:
I had once purchased a teaching kit online to teach others how to play the guitar, it came with a download of material to use. I had a site at www.guitar-lessons-simple-form.com/guitar-backing-tracks.html I had some of the backing tracks for free download for my teaching.

I got this message about a copyright violation. I would have removed the link but I no longer control this website. It belongs to sitesell.com. I have no way of editing the site. The owner of the sitesell is Ken Envoy.

Thank you,

Bryant Dodd
